data.description: Completely remodeled 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home, with large 3+ car detached garage. Private back yard, on a quiet cul de sac lot. Updates include; Exterior siding and insulation in the walls. All new flooring and carpet, trim, interior doors, Kitchen tops, backsplash, appliances, hot water heater, Furnace and central air. Garage roof in 2023, siding in 2018. Bathroom tile, tub, and vanity. Fenced yard with a hot tub. Move in ready.
